.DT
shoplift
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
shoplift

.SH shoplift - Used to steal items from shops
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Syntax
shoplift <object>
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Shoplift is the command you use when you want to steal an item
from a shop.

Your success is affected by your skill, whether you are hiding or not,
and if you have already stolen items in the shop.  You cannot
shoplift while you are in combat.

.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
>shoplift knife
You shoplift the small knife from weapons shop.

>shoplift knife
You tried to steal the small knife from weapons shop but failed.  I wonder if anyone noticed.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
steal
.EP
